verses:
Se wuese wan u i mar Un tswen;
A undu ya u Ter A sen,
A va se a iveren.
Ken hanma ican A kohol se;
ka Wen A yem se sha ku ye;
kwaghNa ne doo u teren.
Oryiman, Tor Huror, Orpaan,
Ter, ka sha ishigh You se lu van,
ser se va gure msen ye;
Ter We U kom icivir ye,
agee Ou hemba sha won je,
ka We u lu Ter tswen ye.

Haleluyah i wuese Ter!
Sugh Aondo Ter ka Un A er
akaa a sha won wuee ye.
I wuese mhoonom Nam sha won;
tom Na u sha won cii ka u doon;
ior sha won cii ve wuese.

Haleluyah i wuese Wan!
Ka un A undu ya Na, man
A yem ior sha won wuee ye;
A kpe sha ciu mbaasorabo,
A nder shin ku i na ve isho;
ior sha won cii ve wuese.

Aondo Ter ka Tor,
Cia nen ne ior;
Aondo ngu a agee,
wuese nen Un kpee;

ijiir na i teman ngi
sha ucerubi;
Aondo mondo iwanger,
sha man tar ve tenger.

M wuese Ter Kristu:
dooshima Na nam mmem.
M yer U mer, Oryima wam;
m ter Un ken igbar.

Ka Un a yimam ye,
A dem isholibo cii;
A doom ishima zanzan je;
M ngu uma ken a Na.

Shin alu ma kwaghbo kpaa una tserem;
ugbaseela man begha kpaa vea ta sha mo

Man zum u me va ar hen pev u kuugh kpaa;
pe ime i we orwasen shio man mo mtsewen tso,
gayo, U ngu a mo kape i doom la.

Ayange a ken hemen kpaa;
de te se kera ga;
We lu orkuran wase gbem;
sha hanmakwagh cica.

Ishima yam men tso Ter Aondo
eren hanmakwagh sha inja;
akaa sha won cii nga karen;
Un yo, luun her gbem sha won.

Iveren i Aondo i sen sha a we;
erdoo Na kpaa alu a we;
A gba akaa a sha won cii;
kwagh hemban Aondo mom ngu ga.

Kwagh ka a doom m gba ember tsuung,
zum u mba lohon ior cii er;
se mough nen je, se mough nen je,
Se kondon nen sha iyou i Ter,
ka Icighanjiir u hemban je,

doo se u tan angahar ker;
Yerusalem pe ior ve kohol
u civir iti i Ter tsuugn la;
ka gar u i maa un kpogholoo;
ka ijiir i hemban i sha won cii.

M ngu nan Ter Aondo jighjigh,A hemba agee sha won;
hanma tom Na ka u doon tseegh,
A gba sha man tar sha won.
Mo kpaa uma wam shin tar ne,
ngu sha ikev Na jimin je;
Un ka Aondo wam man Terem;
ka Un je me civir ye.

M ngu nan Ichighan Jijingi
jighjigh a ishima i mom;
Un ka Aondo mimi mimi;
A va u eren tom u myom;

tem Mbakristu ken asema
ken ityar ityar sha won;
mo kpaa ngum ken ishima gbem je,
hemen mo sha akaadon.

M na jighjigh mer, Ter Aondo
dem kwaghbo wam cica kpaa;
a va nder i shin ku je;
man me lu a uma u tsoron
uma u mimi u Aondo ne.

Mbayev asev cii, ve waan Ter ikyo,
ve de cian ga, ve veren ato;
ve de kera luun er uter vev kpaa ga;
ikyuryan i Ter la ve umbur i ga.

Mo m taver shakwagh Wou je ga,
wea rumun yo, U wasem;
shi taver mo u eren msen,
nahan isholibo i a doom ga;

korom wegh er me gba gayo;
nahan mo kpaa, me gba yemen,
sha ya u Ter a iember.

Kape i lu man sha Golgota;
A kpe sha ciu isholibo yase;
sha Awambe Na i wanger
ishima sha akaabo.

Ican erem je m fa mer me war je ga,
tso m yila Aondo mer, A yimam kpee je;

A ungwa msen wam, mimi je. A yimam;
Ter Aondo hemba sha won jimin cii.

Eren msen gbem, Ter ngu her je,
de deen msen ga, Ngu ungwan we;

Ter tende zwa, eren sha mi;
de deen msen ga, ongo mimi.

Eren msen gbem wuese Ter kpee,
de deen msen ga, doo Un a we;

Ter soo u ungwan, msen wou do Un;
de deen msen ga, Ter ngu rumun.

Ngohol bredi ne cii ya nen;
kape yan U kaa je la
Mo mngu nan ne iyol yam, ya nen;

ngohol wain ne kpaa shi ma nen
kape yan U kaa je la
ka kwagh u umbur Mo mi la.

Ishan i sha Bet'elem je,
doo u kenger i tsuungh je,
lu i va a mbafankwagh ica
ishan i sha Bet'elem tese ikyav je!

Ishan i sha Bet'elem tese ikyav je;
Ishan i sha Bet'elem tese ikyav je;
Ishan i sha Bet'elem tese ikyav je, tese ikyav je;

Terem kpe sha terankon,
ya ican tsuung er Una yimam;
Kwagh Na kumam.
A ya mtsaha wam A paam;
ku je kpaa a kpe ci wam.

Terem kpe sha terankon,
kunya kpa u korom je ga,
Ci Na je ga;
shin a lahan nan nan kpaa;
guda icivir i tar ci i saa.

Yesu nder ngu uma je;
ku u kera cier iyol ga.
Yesu ngu uma, mo kpaa

Una nderem shin ku kera,
me za nyor ken iengem Na;
ka kwagh u tan akperan ga.

Yesu nder ngu teman tor:
tar sha won cii ka tartor Na.
Yan igen se kpaa se ya tor

se lu a Na sha ya Na Sha;
imo Na ia bunde ga;
ka kwagh u tan akperan ga.

Yesu nder, ci wam A kpe;
uma wam ne ngu sha ikev Na,
Una wanger mo wang je,

isholibo kera ya tor je ga,
ngu nan mo agee Na la;
ka kwagh u tan akperan ga.

Yesu nder, mo m fa dedoo;
kwagh paven mo a Na ngu ga
uma, Hade, ku, kwaghbo,

makwagh mom mom sha won kpaa ga;
Yesu Una undum ga;
ka kwagh u tan akperan ga.

Kanyi atoatyev a kumbur yum,
akuraior a yooso daangdang nee;
Utor mba sha won cii ve zough sha num
sar ve ka hendan kwagh a Aondo kpee;

ve zua er a rumun Aondo ga,
kua Un u Aondo A ver Un tor la kpaa;
ve wa kwagh er, se venda nen kwagh Na,
A de ka teman tor mayangega.

A too isholibo yen sha iyol Na;
Wanyongou u Aondo ne (2)x
Yo ember nen Oryiman wen;
Na Un tor (4)x
Na nen Un tor
Wanyongo u Aondo.

Yesu Kristu A va yimam;
Icighan Wan u Aondo ne.

Haleluya, Haleluya

Mo me civir We Oryiman;
kwagh Wou doo hemba cica.

Haleluya, Haleluya

Ka sha ku je, U va yimam;
ka We tseegh me civir ye.

Haleluya, Haleluya

U haa awambe Ou U paam ve;
ka We je, U werem ye.

Haleluya, Haleluya

Ka kwagh kpilighyol je gande;
myom ne hemba sha won cii.

Haleluya, Haleluya

Yesu Terem, We U hemba;
mo me civir We gbem je.

Haleluya, Haleluya

Va hen Ter Yesu,de Timbir ga,
va hen a Na ngu vendan we ga;
Una de isholibo you cica kpa;
de muan ga, va kpee,

De cian Ter ga, dondo sha a Na;
ngu zan a we sha gbenda u sha;
makwagh u hemban Un mom ngu ga;
de timbir ga va kpee.

Mo kpaa bughum hwembe mnger la,
kam pe man u gbem sha won;
man ibyeenegh ki ki yegh la,
ki va hemen mo sha mhoon;
We Oryiman, We Oryiman,
We U lu agee am ye.

Zum u meaa ar hen Yordan la,
hanma mciem ma beem cica;
per a mo shin zegemnger la,
M ar ken tar u Kanaan la;
icam i wuese, icam i wuese,
me de wan We sha won ga.

Se mba dondon Ydesu se fa iime ga;
iwanger i tar ka Yesu!
Ka sea dodndo sha a Na, se lu ken iwanger;
iwanger i tar ka Yesu!

Sha tartor u Aondo iyange ngi ga;
iwanger i sha ka Yesu!
Wanyongo u Aondo kd iwanger i Sha;
iwanger i Sha ka Yesu!

Mo m fa ijiir i waren ga,
ken isheer yam me kor sha We;
shi de undun mo tswen ga,
ivim a agee Ou je;

ka m ver ishima sa we mer;
ka ken We man me war ye;
ken akper a Ou ka ker,
man me yer orhyom wam ye.

Mo kpaa mrumun kwagh Na ve;
Mo kpaa mrumun kwagh Na ve;
Yo se za nen mnzough u ukase,
se za sugh Ter Yesu wase;
Aondo na se Wan Na je;
Kristu Wan u Aondo ne.

Haleluyah kpiligh iyol, Yesu va se a myom cii;
Mhembe... Mhembe...
Isholibo man tahav mbu mhoonom ma Yesu hemba;
Mhembe... Mhembe...

Ger myom wen hanma ijiir yoo bem Na u gbem hanma ijiir;
Mhembe... Mhembe...
se wa nen icam nen icam ne heen, ken ishigh ki hanma orhyom;
Mhembe... Mhembe...

Shin u va hen Yesu er A yima u;
I oo u sha awambe a Na kpaa?
u ngu nan Ter Yesu jighjigh mimi je;
I oo u sha awambe a Na kpa?

Maor ngu saren we u za nengen a nan?
Nan ngu keghen we sha hunda u Sha la;
yo ver ato ungwa imo ngi kaan er;
Saa a vande maren we hegh!

chorus:
Yesu, Yesu ungwa mlyam am ne;
zum u U lu yilan mbagenev yo,
de undun mo ga.

Een tahav cii Yesu wam sha ikyev;
Eee tahav cii Yesu wam sha ikyev;
Yem nen sha won cii za pase nen ior kwaghaondo
Me lu a ven gbem.

verses:
Nenge nen tar cii iime wa va tser ve
uuma kpishi mba va saan ishe;
ka an na za or ior kwagh u Ter Yesu;
nenge nen sha Yesu Ter ker mtser ga.

Aondo Ter ngu kuran tar sha won cica;
ember nen Ter wa nen Un atsaam;
Ter Yesu Una yima se ken ican cii,
ger nen cii; Halleluyah Ter ka Tor.
